[Course_Description]
The business landscape is shifting towards smarter, more digitally connected solutions. In their 2019 book, Reinventing the Product, Eric Schaeffer and David Sovie detail why businesses with more traditional products and workflows should embrace new technologies such as the Internet of Things (IoT), as well as how leaders can create real digital transformation within an organization. This audiobook summary outlines the key points from Reinventing the Product, providing steps you can take to pivot your business towards digital and AI solutions. Learn how to design products as services that keep your customers engaged, incorporate AI into your ecosystem, adapt your current business model for the web, and more. Note: This audiobook summary was produced by Blinkist. We are pleased to host this content in our library.